## Preferences Tab (`preferencesSection`)

### Auto-Save Architecture
All preferences auto-save ‚Äî **no Save button**. A "Saved ‚úì" indicator (`prefsSavedIndicator`) fades in for 2 s on success.

- Slider (`gateThresholdSlider`) fires `input` ‚Üí updates display + `_schedulePreferencesSave()`
- Toggle (`autoGenerateDocsToggle`) fires `change` ‚Üí `_schedulePreferencesSave()`
- Dropdowns (`coverLetterToneSelect`, `resumeLengthSelect`) fire `change` ‚Üí `_schedulePreferencesSave()`
- All share a single 600 ms debounce timer (`_prefsSaveTimer`)

`_schedulePreferencesSave()` ‚Üí debounce ‚Üí `_persistPreferences()` ‚Üí `PATCH /api/v1/profile/preferences`

### Current Preferences

| UI element | Field | Type | Default | Effect |
|-----------|-------|------|---------|--------|
| Range slider | `workflow_gate_threshold` | float 0‚Äì1 | 0.5 | Workflow stops early below this match score |
| Toggle | `auto_generate_documents` | bool | false | When off, user triggers document generation manually |
| Dropdown (inline) | `cover_letter_tone` | str | `professional` | Appends tone instruction to cover letter prompt |
| Dropdown (inline) | `resume_length` | str | `concise` | Appends verbosity instruction to resume advisor prompt |

### Preferences API
```
GET  /api/v1/profile/preferences   ‚Üí ApplicationPreferencesResponse
PATCH /api/v1/profile/preferences  ‚Üí ApplicationPreferencesResponse (partial update, upserts row)
```

Response shape:
```json
{
  "workflow_gate_threshold": 0.5,
  "auto_generate_documents": false,
  "cover_letter_tone": "professional",
  "resume_length": "concise",
  "preferred_model": null,
  "preferred_provider": null
}
```

Switching `preferred_provider` clears `preferred_model`. Model must pass `is_valid_model_for_provider()` in `utils/llm/models.py`.

